OL,3,CRate of women being hired into top
OL,4,Cjobs falls for third year running `
OL,5,CLinkedIn
OL,7,FThe rate of women being hired into UK
OL,8,Fleadership roles has fallen for the
OL,9,Fthird year in a row, with increasing
OL,10,Fbarriers to top jobs as they advance
OL,11,Fthrough their careers, according to
OL,12,Ffigures from LinkedIn.
OL,14,FThe professional networking site
OL,15,Frevealed that women were hired into
OL,16,Fjust more than a third ` 36.8% ` of
OL,17,Fleadership positions in the year to
OL,18,FMarch 1, down 2.1% year-on-year.
