OL,5,CLinkedIn
OL,7,FThis has left the rate of female hires
OL,8,Finto senior roles back where it was in
OL,9,F2020, according to the figures.
OL,11,FThe data also showed that while more
OL,12,FUK women are now in top management
OL,13,Froles than they were in 2019 ` at
OL,14,F30.9% last year versus 27.6% in 2019 `
OL,15,Fthe progress has slowed significantly
OL,16,Fin the past two years, rising by just
OL,17,F0.3 percentage points.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
