OL,3,CRate of women being hired into top
OL,4,Cjobs falls for third year running `
OL,5,CLinkedIn
OL,7,FGlobally, the figures paint a similar
OL,8,Fpicture, revealing that less than a
OL,9,Fthird of senior leadership roles are
OL,10,Fheld by women (30.9%) despite making
OL,11,Fup almost half (43.2%) of the
OL,12,Fworldwide workforce.
OL,14,FThis "drop to the top" is most
OL,15,Fpronounced in the science, technology,
OL,16,Fengineering and mathematics (Stem)
OL,17,Fsector, where only around one in eight
OL,18,F(12%) of leadership positions are held
OL,19,Fby women, according to LinkedIn.
