OL,5,CLinkedIn
OL,7,FIt is calling for the Government and
OL,8,Fbusinesses to promote hiring based on
OL,9,Fskills rather than qualifications to
OL,10,Fhelp ensure women do not get left
OL,11,Fbehind, in particular amid the shift
OL,12,Ftowards artificial intelligence (AI).
OL,14,FJanine Chamberlin, head of LinkedIn
OL,15,FUK, said: "Just as AI is reshaping the
OL,16,Fworkplace and demanding more
OL,17,Fadaptable, collaborative leadership,
OL,18,Fwe're seeing women's progress into
OL,19,Fsenior roles stall for the third year
OL,20,Frunning.
