OL,7,F"Women are 20% more likely to have
OL,8,Fthat multi-domain experience, working
OL,9,Facross different industries and
OL,10,Ffunctions, which creates exactly the
OL,11,Fkind of flexible, agile leaders
OL,12,Fbusinesses need for AI transformation.
OL,14,F"Yet we're locking them out of
OL,15,Fleadership precisely when we need
OL,16,Fthose skills most."
